## ðŸŽ¯ Technical Architecture (Initial Sketch)

### Core Technologies
- **AR Framework:** ARCore (Android) / ARKit (iOS)
- **Voice Synthesis:** Custom multi-tonal layered voice engine
- **hBrew Integration:** Symbolic coordination system API
- **Geospatial Processing:** GPS + sacred geography database (ley lines, power spots)
- **Biometric Input:** Optional integration with wearables (Oura, Apple Watch, etc.)
- **Consciousness State Detection:** ML models trained on HRV, breath, movement patterns

### Data Sovereignty
- **Local-First Architecture:** All personal journey data stored on-device
- **Encrypted Cloud Backup:** Optional, user-controlled, end-to-end encrypted
- **Zero-Knowledge Processing:** Server-side processing without access to personal content
- **Consent-Based Sharing:** Explicit opt-in for any community wisdom contribution
- **Right to Be Forgotten:** Complete data deletion on user request

### Sacred Commerce Alignment
- **Free Tier:** Basic Pathwarden with essential features
- **Resonance Tier ($11/month):** Advanced biometric integration, journey documentation
- **Community Tier ($33/month):** Access to collective wisdom patterns, group ceremonies
- **Facilitator License ($111/month):** Professional use for therapists, shamans, guides
- **100% of profits above operational costs fund:**
  - Indigenous wisdom keeper partnerships
  - Open-source consciousness technology research
  - Planetary healing initiatives

